                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Tower</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-02-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 17, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Tower reports that he has conveyed to the Emperor the profound appreciation
                    of the President of his initiative and cooperation in the matter of Chinese
                    neutrality, and that the Emperor was exceedingly gratified and expressed most
                    friendly sentiments toward the President.)</p>
            </div>
